{"tid":2026731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美售台MK48重型魚雷  可高速擊毀共軍航母   環球時報 : 「不知從哪個垃圾堆翻出來的」","createTime":"2020-05-21T06:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:26:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":121,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"b6c36d34de331e2bdec55c0d07fca48ba9b6046c","tid":2026731,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"總統蔡英文昨（ 20 ）進行就職宣誓，美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）主動聲明恭賀總統連任，今（ 21 ）日上午更送上「賀禮」，宣布再度售台 18 枚 MK-48 AT Mod 6 重型魚雷，不過中國軍系官媒隨即發文狠酸，「不知從哪個垃圾堆翻出來的」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院政治軍事局（ U.S. Department of State's Bureau of Political-Military Affairs ）今宣布，國務院已批准對台軍售，包括 18 枚 MK-48 AT Mod 6 重型魚雷，以及備料、支援與測試設備、運輸器、培訓與技術後勤支援等，此軍售也已由美國國防安全合作署（DSCA）正式通知國會。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國鷹派軍系官媒《環球時報》隨即發文，聲稱軍售消息引起「島內網友的不滿」，報導藉由部分台灣網友的留言嘲諷「台灣錢真好賺」、「好貴呀，確定不是二手貨？」、「不知道從哪個垃圾堆裡翻出來的」等。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美軍目前最新重型魚雷為 MK-48 AT Mod 7 ，但僅供應北約（ NATO ）成員如荷蘭、加拿大，以及與美合作發展 Mod 7 的澳洲海軍，其餘國家所能獲得的最先進型號就是本次售台的 MK-48 AT Mod 6 重型魚雷。值得注意的是，台灣 2017 年就已曾購得 46 枚該型魚雷，因此本次美國也並非首次售台該型魚雷，正如美國務院新聞稿所言「不會改變區域的軍事平衡」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%94%AE%E5%8F%B0mk48%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7-%E5%8F%AF%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%93%8A%E6%AF%80%E5%85%B1%E8%BB%8D%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92-%E8%AA%9E%E7%8B%A0%E9%85%B8-042350998.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%258F%25B0mk48%25E9%25AD%259A%25E9%259B%25B7-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2580%259F%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2588%25AA%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%25AA%259E%25E7%258B%25A0%25E9%2585%25B8-042350998.html&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=bda9c298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%94%AE%E5%8F%B0mk48%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7-%E5%8F%AF%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%93%8A%E6%AF%80%E5%85%B1%E8%BB%8D%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92-%E8%AA%9E%E7%8B%A0%E9%85%B8-042350998.html</a>"},{"pid":"87c36d2ac194bdba1f41309d8a72fa8701cc4a0d","tid":2026731,"uid":177089,"like":70,"dislike":7,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"支那仔唔夠人打：垃圾！<br />\n<br />\n連登仔唔夠人串：垃圾！"},{"pid":"2d7d76d944784571d1a940194f2cc65849347c10","tid":2026731,"uid":276609,"like":157,"dislike":2,"score":155,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"遼寧艦咪就係人地唔要的垃圾"},{"pid":"705c9cd4926f499256e1489b54aab76d91b7231b","tid":2026731,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e019e3ccc679a56b0b428d81b9fb60de063e8b","tid":2026731,"uid":316,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾舊玩具都夠炸沉遼寧艦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40da8febc387d5e4a20868c396bc20ab2eb40cd","tid":2026731,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ed1ca5c194245089e230b825ec0b4f1ae5bf47","tid":2026731,"uid":72304,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"2d7d76d944784571d1a940194f2cc65849347c10","tid":2026731,"uid":276609,"like":157,"dislike":2,"score":155,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"遼寧艦咪就係人地唔要的垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"「支那錢真好賺」、「好貴呀，確定不是二手貨？」、「不知道從哪個垃圾堆裡翻出來的」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c918bb3b82cb000668135d16daf3a56261edb8","tid":2026731,"uid":253978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://