:"2020-05-21T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"有錢佬法拉利換新車林寶<br />\n跟手賣架架舊車法拉利比人，咁架法拉利係唔係垃圾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a3038f5b40be941923da7cb87c2cab5d21e56d","tid":2026731,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"買不到的魚雷是垃圾的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cef08c7ca50d53cfb477f11986e31529aaf3403","tid":2026731,"uid":73741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6f63aa6ef3d4788d9b5e0b69b1085719da6ea460","tid":2026731,"uid":137159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55acf9fcf6ac9e9e39b6e856b461b32bd5a1ed85","tid":2026731,"uid":3480,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://photo.sina.cn/album_8_198_3913.htm?ch=8&amp;from=wap&amp;vt=4&amp;hd=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphoto.sina.cn%2Falbum_8_198_3913.htm%3Fch%3D8%26from%3Dwap%26vt%3D4%26hd%3D1&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=74e3b367\" target=\"_blank\">https://photo.sina.cn/album_8_198_3913.htm?ch=8&amp;from=wap&amp;vt=4&amp;hd=1</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸網<br />\n不過隻dd食左一飛都斷兩截<br />\n何況中國濕鳩船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"潛水艇用重型魚雷。美軍研發目的係對付蘇聯核潛艇，今次台灣買黎似係用嚟對付支那航母或者大型登陸艦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"美國魚雷聲納尋標頭技術全球領先，不嬲都可水下水面兩用，開發嗰陣嗰要求係可以打沉蘇聯30節核潛艇同水面巡洋艦"},{"pid":"6d2afc4b778592ee05d02b7a57cbb095cfe170d4","tid":2026731,"uid":192212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6c36d34de331e2bdec55c0d07fca48ba9b6046c","tid":2026731,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"總統蔡英文昨（ 20 ）進行就職宣誓，美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）主動聲明恭賀總統連任，今（ 21 ）日上午更送上「賀禮」，宣布再度售台 18 枚 MK-48 AT Mod 6 重型魚雷，不過中國軍系官媒隨即發文狠酸，「不知從哪個垃圾堆翻出來的」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院政治軍事局（ U.S. Department of State's Bureau of Political-Military Affairs ）今宣布，國務院已批准對台軍售，包括 18 枚 MK-48 AT Mod 6 重型魚雷，以及備料、支援與測試設備、運輸器、培訓與技術後勤支援等，此軍售也已由美國國防安全合作署（DSCA）正式通知國會。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國鷹派軍系官媒《環球時報》隨即發文，聲稱軍售消息引起「島內網友的不滿」，報導藉由部分台灣網友的留言嘲諷「台灣錢真好賺」、「好貴呀，確定不是二手貨？」、「不知道從哪個垃圾堆裡翻出來的」等。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美軍目前最新重型魚雷為 MK-48 AT Mod 7 ，但僅供應北約（ NATO ）成員如荷蘭、加拿大，以及與美合作發展 Mod 7 的澳洲海軍，其餘國家所能獲得的最先進型號就是本次售台的 MK-48 AT Mod 6 重型魚雷。值得注意的是，台灣 2017 年就已曾購得 46 枚該型魚雷，因此本次美國也並非首次售台該型魚雷，正如美國務院新聞稿所言「不會改變區域的軍事平衡」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%94%AE%E5%8F%B0mk48%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7-%E5%8F%AF%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%93%8A%E6%AF%80%E5%85%B1%E8%BB%8D%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92-%E8%AA%9E%E7%8B%A0%E9%85%B8-042350998.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%258F%25B0mk48%25E9%25AD%259A%25E9%259B%25B7-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2580%259F%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2588%25AA%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%25AA%259E%25E7%258B%25A0%25E9%2585%25B8-042350998.html&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=bda9c298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%94%AE%E5%8F%B0mk48%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7-%E5%8F%AF%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%93%8A%E6%AF%80%E5%85%B1%E8%BB%8D%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92-%E8%AA%9E%E7%8B%A0%E9%85%B8-042350998.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"B52都差唔多70年<br />\n美軍仲用緊"},{"pid":"307df03bddb6c10d1e094a652e1690baea8ec3f9","tid":2026731,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"遼寧號咪係佢俄爸的二手貨"},{"pid":"dfb14aa0137090d6efc33c4fa6207f41e5072a09","tid":2026731,"uid":13914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"福克蘭群島戰爭<br />\n貝爾格拉諾將軍號巡洋艦<br />\n只要打得中識爆炸, 垃圾都一樣可以打沉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj